&lt;p&gt;It is pretty hard to make a generic function to handle this well. You will often spend as much code converting &lt;code&gt;[]int&lt;/code&gt; to &lt;code&gt;[]interface{}&lt;/code&gt; and back, as it is to just copy the snippet. I do have a slightly nicer way to do it though:&lt;/p&gt;

