&lt;p&gt;Simply using an &lt;code&gt;interface{}&lt;/code&gt; which is what &lt;a href="http://golang.org/pkg/encoding/json/#Decoder.Decode" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;code&gt;Decoder.Decode&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; uses anyway, for &lt;a href="http://play.golang.org/p/b1YAGU6C_b" rel="nofollow"&gt;example&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

